Title: Enacts the New York state food security purchase and processing act; appropriation
Summary: Enacts the New York state food security purchase and processing act to establish a state-level program that purchases food grown or raised by New York farmers; requires processing within New York State; distributes such food to communities in need.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law, in relation to enacting the New York state food security purchase and processing act; and making an appropriation therefor
